<D>__{what do you think's going on? hobson died.}
<C>__{vivienne}
<D>__{oh, that.}
<A>__{she bustles in past arthur. a platoon of maids follows.}
<C>__{vivienne }
<P>__{(to maids)}
<D>__{chop chop! you cleany penthouseio! come on, arthur. have to pick yourself up, lad. it's like when nixon my great dane had to be put down. frightful state for days. but i pulled myself together.}
<C>__{arthur}
<D>__{you're comparing hobson to...a dog?}
